    XXSSeettWWMMNNoorrmmaallHHiinnttss can generate BadAlloc and BadWindow errors.

    The XXGGeettWWMMNNoorrmmaallHHiinnttss function returns the size hints stored in the
    WM_NORMAL_HINTS property on the specified window. If the property is of
