    an old (pre-ICCCM) or new size hints structure, XXGGeettWWMMNNoorrmmaallHHiinnttss sets the
    various fields of the XXSSiizzeeHHiinnttss structure, sets the supplied_return
    argument to the list of fields that were supplied by the user (whether or
